name: EndnoteTextFrames

properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

parameters.name: layer
parameters.description: The layer on which to create the EndnoteTextFrame. (Optional)

parameters.name: at
parameters.description: The location at which to insert the EndnoteTextFrame relative to the reference object or within the container object. (Optional)

parameters.name: reference
parameters.description: The reference object. Note: Required when the at parameter is before or after. Can accept: Document, Spread, MasterSpread, Page, Layer or PageItem. (Optional)

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new EndnoteTextFrame (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the EndnoteTextFrame.

methods.name: item

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrame with the specified index or name.

methods.name: itemByName
methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrame with the specified name.

methods.name: itemByID
methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrame with the specified ID.

methods.name: itemByRange

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The EndnoteTextFrame, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: EndnoteTextFrame, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The EndnoteTextFrame, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: EndnoteTextFrame, Long Integer or String.

methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrames within the specified range.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the EndnoteTextFrame that follows the desired EndnoteTextFrame.

methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrame with the index previous to the specified index.

methods.name: nextItem

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The EndnoteTextFrame whose index comes before the desired EndnoteTextFrame.

methods.description: Returns the EndnoteTextFrame whose index follows the specified EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every EndnoteTextFrame in the collection.

methods.name: toSource
methods.description: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the EndnoteTextFrame.
Returns the EndnoteTextFrame with the specified index.

description: A collection of endnote text frames.
